snippet.title: Bay Area Goretti Group
snippet.description: The Goretti Group is a movement for people of all ages and states in life seeking to rediscover authentic masculinity and femininity and become witnesses to the joy of pure love. Founded in honor of St. Maria Goretti, the patron saint of chastity, this channel will cover topics related to dating, courtship, and marriage, as well as mental health, forgiveness, and healing, and how we live out these aspects of our lives, in light of Catholic teaching.
